msgid ""
"The Qubes OS website content is stored in the `qubesos.github.io "
"<https://github.com/QubesOS/qubesos.github.io>`__ repository and its "
"submodules. By cloning and regularly pulling from this repo, users can "
"maintain their own up-to-date offline copy of the Qubes OS website rather"
" than relying solely on the web."
