"was converted from Markdown to reStructuredText and remains as a guide if"
" you want to contribute to the Qubes OS website. If you want to "
"contribute to the Qubes OS documentation, please visit :doc:`How to edit "
"the documentation </developer/general/how-to-edit-the-rst-"
