#: ../../developer/general/how-to-edit-the-website.rst:27
#: 3e7e00b8453942faba43b1f8cb9d67f5
msgid ""
"Since Qubes is a security-oriented project, every change will be "
"`reviewed <#security>`__ before it’s accepted. This allows us to maintain"
" quality control and protect our users."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/general/how-to-edit-the-website.rst:28
#: a389c5a78bc244de97b39ff0934485da
msgid ""
"To give your contribution a better chance of being accepted, please "
"follow our :doc:`website style guide </developer/general/website-style-"
"guide>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/general/how-to-edit-the-website.rst:29
#: 64549e2e30ae437aa818b2cf40c8f3ae
msgid ""
"We don’t want you to spend time and effort on a contribution that we "
"can’t accept. If your contribution would take a lot of time, please "
":doc:`file an issue </introduction/issue-tracking>` for it first so that "
"we can make sure we’re on the same page before significant works begins."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/general/how-to-edit-the-website.rst:30
#: 3712da049fbd45a8a34a5d9cf25f1807
msgid ""
