"would be beneficial to the Qubes community, please consider adding it to "
"the :doc:`documentation </developer/general/how-to-edit-the-rst-"
"documentation>` or the :ref:`external documentation <developer/general"
"/rst-documentation-style-guide:core vs. external documentation>`."
msgstr ""

